      <title>股票飙升后，Intesa 成为欧盟最大的上市银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/intesa-becomes-eu-s-largest-listed-lender-after-stock-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合圣保罗银行 (Intesa Sanpaolo SpA) 首次以市值成为欧盟最大的银行，在今年该意大利银行股价飙升之后，该银行超过了西班牙桑坦德银行 (Banco Santander SA)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/intesa-becomes-eu-s-largest-listed-lender-after-stock-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台风“克拉通”导致台湾市值 2.5 万亿美元的股市关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/typhoon-krathon-shuts-taiwan-s-2-5-trillion-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着超强台风“克拉通”带着强风和暴雨逼近台湾，台湾将关闭价值 2.5 万亿美元的股票市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/typhoon-krathon-shuts-taiwan-s-2-5-trillion-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:19:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯钢铁亿万富翁进军婴儿食品行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/russian-steel-billionaire-branches-out-to-popular-baby-food</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯最大钢铁公司的老板、亿万富翁弗拉基米尔·利辛 (Vladimir Lisin) 同意收购一家在当地与百事可乐公司 (PepsiCo Inc.) 竞争的婴儿食品生产商，以实现其在俄罗斯境内业务组合的多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/russian-steel-billionaire-branches-out-to-popular-baby-food</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，Adani Flagship 的 13 亿美元股票出售将于下周开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/adani-flagship-s-1-3-billion-share-sale-said-to-start-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的旗舰公司计划最早于下周开始出售其股票，标志着该公司重返公开股票市场。此前，2023 年的一份严厉的卖空者报告破坏了之前的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/adani-flagship-s-1-3-billion-share-sale-said-to-start-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>燃料价格下跌后巴基斯坦通胀进一步放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/pakistan-inflation-slows-further-as-government-cuts-fuel-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政府大幅削减燃料价格且食品成本下降后，巴基斯坦 9 月份通胀率降至近四年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/pakistan-inflation-slows-further-as-government-cuts-fuel-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 09:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
