      <title>飓风海伦导致芯片制造所需的石英矿停产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/hurricane-helene-halts-silbelco-s-quartz-mine-in-north-carolina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风海伦导致北卡罗来纳州的采矿业务暂停，该业务生产用于制造半导体硅片的高纯度石英。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/hurricane-helene-halts-silbelco-s-quartz-mine-in-north-carolina</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 00:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
